明请求处理的延迟增加。\n   - 证据：`rrt`, `rrt_max`。\n\n### 输出 JSON\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"client_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\", \"server_error_ratio\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in error_ratio and server_error_ratio indicating a potential service issue.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Metrics show error_ratio and server_error_ratio change rate of 2.0.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increase in error_ratio, client_error_ratio, and pod_cpu_usage suggesting resource consumption and error hike.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Metrics error_ratio, client_error_ratio, and pod_cpu_usage have elevated values.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increase in server_error_ratio and error_ratio indicating potential cache layer problems.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Metrics server_error_ratio and error_ratio show significant changes.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Rising client_error_ratio and error_ratio suggest upstream call errors.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Metrics client_error_ratio and error_ratio are significantly high.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increases in rrt and rrt_max pointing to processing delays.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Metrics rrt and rrt_max significantly increased.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
